14
00:02:17,311 --> 00:02:19,905
Okay. But can you do it fast?

15
00:02:19,981 --> 00:02:24,680
You know, this doesn't look good.
None of this looks good at all.

16
00:02:24,752 --> 00:02:27,448
Well, thanks very much, Dr. Nichols.

17
00:02:27,522 --> 00:02:31,117
You've really been a great help.
You've been a great doctor.

18
00:02:31,192 --> 00:02:33,717
Well, thank you.

19
00:02:35,363 --> 00:02:37,297
Can you hand me my bag, please?

20
00:02:41,035 --> 00:02:43,299
See ya.

21
00:02:43,371 --> 00:02:46,306
Hey, Anthony, don't try
to save everybody, okay?

22
00:02:46,374 --> 00:02:48,342
Okay, I won't.

23
00:02:51,179 --> 00:02:52,737
Dennis!

24
00:02:56,184 --> 00:02:58,778
- See ya later, Felicia.
- Hey, Anthony. Thanks for everything.

25
00:02:58,853 --> 00:03:01,287
- Good-bye. Take care.
- Bye, Barbara.

26
00:03:01,355 --> 00:03:03,789
- See ya, Chris.
- Thanks, Anthony.

27
00:03:03,858 --> 00:03:07,385
Come on. Any problems?
Yes! Wonderful.

28
00:03:07,462 --> 00:03:09,657
Wait, wait.
Who'd you get to do that?

29
00:03:09,731 --> 00:03:12,598
Did you bribe the janitor?
Smart.

30
00:03:21,743 --> 00:03:23,677
- Driver, what's our E.T.A.?
- 7:30.

31
00:03:23,745 --> 00:03:26,543
Good. We're on schedule. Here's
our agenda for the next few months.

32
00:03:26,614 --> 00:03:29,674
- You'll find everything is in order.
- Practice job. Looks good.

33
00:03:29,751 --> 00:03:33,380
That's our first move when we get back.
Look it over. I'll brief you on the way.

34
00:03:33,454 --> 00:03:37,584
This is what I was trying to do.

35
00:03:37,658 --> 00:03:39,649
The practice job, a heist.

36
00:03:39,727 --> 00:03:41,922
You and I both respond to goals.

37
00:03:41,996 --> 00:03:44,123
- It all leads to Mr. Henry.
- The guy from the letters.

38
00:03:44,198 --> 00:03:46,598
Exactly. This is rough.

39
00:03:46,667 --> 00:03:49,329
You and I respond to structure...

40
00:03:49,403 --> 00:03:52,201
and that's what's important.

41
00:03:52,273 --> 00:03:54,264
"The next 50."

42
00:03:56,544 --> 00:04:00,139
So, did you enjoy your first
visit to the nuthouse?

43
00:04:00,214 --> 00:04:03,206
Come on. Be sensitive to the fact
that other people...

44
00:04:03,284 --> 00:04:06,617
are not comfortable talking
about emotional disturbances.

45
00:04:08,122 --> 00:04:11,057
You know I am. I'm fine with that.
But other people...

46
00:04:11,125 --> 00:04:13,491
Put it behind you.
You're out. You're better.

47
00:04:13,561 --> 00:04:16,530
- You're right.
- And so it begins.

48
00:04:16,597 --> 00:04:20,158
Now, we should also get on a fitness
regime... sit-ups, hitting the bags...

49
00:04:20,234 --> 00:04:22,759
