when I was in the desert.

50
00:04:22,837 --> 00:04:26,898
Were you really?
That's good cardiovascular.

51
00:04:26,974 --> 00:04:29,807
When did you get so avid
about the fitness thing, Dignan?

52
00:04:29,877 --> 00:04:33,142
What? What do you mean by avid?

53
00:04:33,214 --> 00:04:35,978
I've never known you
to be all that athletic.

54
00:04:36,050 --> 00:04:38,211
You've never known me
to be all that athletic?

55
