01:25:38,374 --> 01:25:40,569
- Thanks.
- We did it though, didn't we?

1171
01:25:44,914 --> 01:25:47,508
Yeah, we did it, all right.

1172
01:25:53,423 --> 01:25:56,017
Well, thank you for comin'.

1173
01:25:58,928 --> 01:26:00,520
It's good seein' you.

1174
01:26:04,333 --> 01:26:07,598
- Did you bring that grappling hook?
- Grappling hook?

1175
01:26:07,670 --> 01:26:09,729
I think I might have found
a way out of here.

1176
01:26:09,806 --> 01:26:12,240
- You're kidding!
- No, I'm not.

1177
01:26:12,308 --> 01:26:15,209
- How?
- Wait for my instructions.

1178
01:26:16,245 --> 01:26:18,941
When we go through the next gate, you'll
have 30 seconds to take out the guard.

1179
01:26:19,015 --> 01:26:20,073
- What?
- 30 seconds!

1180
01:26:20,149 --> 01:26:22,447
Have the car running
at the northwest checkpoint.

1181
01:26:22,518 --> 01:26:26,386
- Bob and I will scale the barricade.
- Hold on!

1182
01:26:26,456 --> 01:26:30,916
And Bob, remember, shield me from
the bullets! They won't shoot civilians!

1183
01:26:30,993 --> 01:26:32,790
- Are you ready?
- Hold on!

1184
01:26:32,862 --> 01:26:35,888
Let's go! Now!

1185
01:26:42,305 --> 01:26:45,672
Isn't it funny how you used to be
in the nuthouse and now I'm in jail?

